==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chicanery
<hw>Chi*can"er*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>chicanerie</ets>.]</ety> <def>Mean or unfair artifice to perplex a
cause and obscure the truth; stratagem; sharp practice;
sophistry.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Irritated by perpetual <qex>chicanery</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Hallam.</qau></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Trickery; sophistry; stratagem.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chiccory</ent>⟦br⟧
